:"","children":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2178416778","tinyui":"/x/igDYgQ","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2178416778","webui":"/spaces/BAN/overview","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2178416778"}},{"id":"2259944189","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2259944189","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjI1OTk0NDE4OQ==","status":"current","title":"Documentación Técnica","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":44304616},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2259944189/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2259944189/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2259944189/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2259944189/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2259944189","tinyui":"/x/-QK0hg","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2259944189","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2259944189/Documentaci+n+T+cnica","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2259944189"}},{"id":"3304751116","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/3304751116","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMzMwNDc1MTExNg==","status":"current","title":"Iniciando un nuevo proyecto Angus","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":682218221},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3304751116/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3304751116/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3304751116/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3304751116/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3304751116","tinyui":"/x/DID6x","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3304751116","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3304751116/Iniciando+un+nuevo+proyecto+Angus","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3304751116"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<p>Desde la perspectiva de SRE existen varias iniciativas que deben ser implementadas en la primer versi&oacute;n de cada proyecto nuevo. A continuaci&oacute;n las listamos y adjuntamos algunas indicaciones de c&oacute;mo implementarlas.</p><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"toc\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"407a3d5f-1cad-4e86-a11a-ad547988a17c\" ac:macro-id=\"5b697dbc-f0f6-48a5-a81e-f220ac21c9a8\"><ac:parameter ac:name=\"style\">none</ac:parameter></ac:structured-macro><h2>Configuraci&oacute;n de redis</h2><p>El redis debe configurarse con <code>keepalived</code> para seguir un esquema activo-pasivo. De esta manera van a participar dos nodos de redis (el activo o master y el pasivo o slave) y una IP flotante que va a estar asignada al nodo master.</p><p>En caso de un fallo en el nodo activo, el nodo pasivo tomar&aacute; poseci&oacute;n de la IP flotante y la instancia slave de Redis ser&aacute; promovida a master.</p><p>El set up requiere cambios en los repositorios del servicio, de <code>bancard-docker</code> y en <code>bancard-configurations</code>. El detalle lo podemos ver <a href=\"https://bancard.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/PRYSRE/pages/114032836/Setup+REDIS+HA+con+keepalived\">ac&aacute;</a>.</p><h2>Dockerizaci&oacute;n de nginx</h2><p>La dockerizaci&oacute;n de nginx aporta un control aislado de todo lo que tenga que ver con este componente. Esto permite gestionar la versi&oacute;n de nginx desde la imagen del contenedor, la configuraci&oacute;n va a estar directamente en el contenedor tambi&eacute;n, y separada del server. </p><p>Aqu&iacute; es importante gestionar bien los archivos de configuraci&oacute;n que son com&uacute;nes entre los servicios que corren en cada server. </p><p>El repositorio va a tener una copia de los archivos que en el server est&aacute; en <code>/etc/nginx/conf.d/</code> y una del archivo de configuraci&oacute;n propio de cada servicio que el server tiene en <code>/etc/nginx/sites-available/</code>.</p><p>Hay cambios que se aplican en el action, para buildear los certificados y la imagen de nginx, y es importante asegurar que a la hora de desplegar, se debe utilizar el flag <code>-k nginx</code> en el comando <code>bancard-deploy</code>.</p><p>M&aacute;s detalles <a href=\"https://bancard.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/PRYSRE/pages/316145682/Dockerizaci+n+de+nginx\">ac&aacute;</a>.</p><h2>Mejoras en actions</h2><p>Los cambios en los actions se han hecho buscando mejoras en los tiempos y costos a la hora de buildear las imagenes que corresponden a cada proyecto. </p><p>En una etapa inicial, se unificaron los archivos <code>Dockerfile.base</code> y <code>Dockerfile.prod</code>en los proyectos para crear una sola imagen, y se separar la creaci&oacute;n de la imagen del servicio de la de los dem&aacute;s componentes (nginx, redis, etc), la vez de condicionar esta &uacute;ltima para que solo se inicie al hacer push a <code>master</code> o a <code>develop</code></p><p>Este cambio require modificaciones en <code>Dockerfile.base</code>, eliminar <code>Dockerfile.prod</code> y modificar bastante los actions. </p><p>M&aacute;s detalles <a href=\"https://bancard.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/PRYSRE/pages/1483604614/Optimizaci+n+de+Actions\">ac&aacute;</a>.</p>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/4281761851"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":156},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/4281761851/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/4281761851/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/4281761851/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/4281761851/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=4281761851","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/4281761851/Configuraci+n+del+proyecto+nuevo+-+SRE","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/4281761851","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/4281761851","tinyui":"/x/O4A2-w","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}